{"tid":918492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【睇片】新疆再教育營內部曝光　證鐵閘囚室與監獄無異","createTime":"2018-11-27T09:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T14:13:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7747deaf0ead84f0db2e8eec577710f6de945e","tid":918492,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uQHuOfKgNsI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuQHuOfKgNsI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=LFry4mU5MBWBgVoBxpk3xdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=d12b0ed9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uQHuOfKgNsI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.55.4020PM20copy_ufXIA_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.55.4020PM20copy_ufXIA_1200x0.png&h=1b36a5fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.55.3520PM20copy_tRKyh_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.55.3520PM20copy_tRKyh_1200x0.png&h=7210e167&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.57.0520PM20copy_DfFvC_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.57.0520PM20copy_DfFvC_1200x0.png&h=75e569cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.56.3920PM20copy_8lkDC_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.56.3920PM20copy_8lkDC_1200x0.png&h=14ff503f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.56.3720PM20copy_PvAdL_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202018-11-2720at2012.56.3720PM20copy_PvAdL_1200x0.png&h=44a32f3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共近年大規模抓捕新疆穆斯林並將他們關押在「再教育營」內，惟官方一直宣稱這些設施只是「職業培訓中心」。關注中國人權問題的網站《寒冬》昨日發表影片，罕有地公開了再教育營內部情況，證實營內房間被重重鐵閘包圍，每個角落都被閉路電視監控，所謂「職業培訓中心」根本就與監獄無異。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《寒冬》昨日發表報道，稱收到一名記者傳來影片，拍攝到新疆再教育營內部情況。影片可見，營內有多棟橙色建築物，為被關押人士的住處。這些四層高的建築物上，所有窗戶都有鐵欄包圍著。每個建築物入口都有三個閉路電視監控，並設有鐵閘，大廈外牆則寫著「衷心感謝以習近平同志為核心的黨中央」等字眼。<br />\n<br />\n影片可見，建築物內部近乎與監獄無異，每間房間都設有雙重鐵閘，門外設有密碼鎖。每間囚室都有洗手間，全部被閉路電視監控。報道引述內部消息指，建築物內每層有28間囚室及3個課室，每個囚室可以住15人。<br />\n<br />\n在建築物內，牆上亦印有大量口號，包括是「讓學國語成為一種習慣」、「在習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想指引下，為實現中華民族偉大復興的中國夢不懈奮鬥」。大廈內亦設有一個監控室，內有一個巨型屏幕播放著閉路電視畫面。<br />\n<br />\n在大廈前方的空地，有多個被鐵絲網包圍的空間，上面寫著「應急避險場所」。不過報道引述消息指，這些「避險場所」實際上是讓被囚人士行走、做運動的戶外空間，與一般監獄的做法相同。<br />\n<br />\n新疆再教育營近期引起國際社會關注，不少外國媒體都試圖到新疆採訪，但往往被防範嚴密的國保阻止。因此以往的報道，通常都是依賴衛星圖片拍攝再教育營。今次的影片，是罕有地拍攝到營內具體情況。<br />\n<br />\n今年8月聯合國消除種族歧視委員會曾舉行聆訊，委員會成員 Gay McDougall 在會上稱有大量可靠的報告指出，內地約有100萬名維吾爾族人被關柙在營內，指中國以打擊宗教極端主義和維持社會穩定為名，將新疆自治區變成秘密的大型拘禁營。不過中國一直宣稱，這些設施只是「職業教育和就業培訓中心」，讓當地人學習技能融入社會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%86%8D%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%87%9F%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E8%AD%89%E9%90%B5%E9%96%98%E5%9B%9A%E5%AE%A4%E8%88%87%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E7%84%A1%E7%95%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%25AD%2589%25E9%2590%25B5%25E9%2596%2598%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%258D%2584%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2595%25B0%2F&d=LFry4mU5MBWBgVoBxpk3xdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a675577f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%25AD%2589%25E9%2590%25B5%25E9%2596%2598%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%258D%2584%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2595%25B0%2F&h=4948500c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%86%8D%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%87%9F%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E8%AD%89%E9%90%B5%E9%96%98%E5%9B%9A%E5%AE%A4%E8%88%87%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E7%84%A1%E7%95%B0/</a>"},{"pid":"ab5edfe9b7d32c307600b9a06f0059f8e595a2cc","tid":918492,"uid":198595,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"香港幾時先捉啲南亞狗咁做 對住伊斯蘭唔咁做唔得"},{"pid":"ec399ca57c771dd6545268a9322fc7b209113dd0","tid":918492,"uid":79563,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180215/d47e199572ec496cbd67914c4183a2b2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180215%2Fd47e199572ec496cbd67914c4183a2b2.jpeg&h=970596e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92bec3d2e48b2dc0ef6de8f4c97d0c2825fa869","tid":918492,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ab5edfe9b7d32c307600b9a06f0059f8e595a2cc","tid":918492,"uid":198595,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"香港幾時先捉啲南亞狗咁做 對住伊斯蘭唔咁做唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"應該整隻病毒